\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93What are you doing here?\'94 the killer asked him. Jonathan noticed that though his tone was threatening, his voice was high in pitch, almost feminine.
\f1\fs20 \

\f0\fs24 \'93I heard gunfire,\'94 Jonathan told him, just barely managing to keep his voice even.
\f1\fs20 \
